edding, LLM re-ranking) sequenced with System infrastructure (vector DB, network).","test_description":"Execute 100+ real end-to-end queries through the full pipeline: (1) call embedding API on diverse queries, (2) search the real vector DB, (3) fetch top-K results, (4) call real LLM re-ranker, (5) serialize and return response. Measure wall-clock latency for each query. Compute the median latency and verify it is < 2000 ms. Log the 50th, 75th, 95th, and 99th percentile latencies. Vary query complexity and result set sizes to ensure the SLA holds under realistic conditions.","plan_consistent":true,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0,"Integration":0.05,"System":0.15,"Agentic":0.05,"Workflow":0.75}}]},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13643,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":13643},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fee3e0bc-75bd-41fb-84fb-60fc4aa439dd","uuid":"4268c480-dc89-4a84-a290-20c1f39109e4"}
